name: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
desc: Constants that represent message values for the entry message filters.

items.name: static let convertExclude: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the conversion operation has skipped the entry as the path data is an archive header instance.

items.name: static let decodeReading: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the decoder operation is reading the entry at path.

items.name: static let encodeScanning: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the encoder operation is scanning the entry at path.

items.name: static let encodeWriting: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the encoder operation is writing the entry at path.

items.name: static let extractACL: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the extraction operation has modified entry access control lists.

items.name: static let extractAttributes: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the extraction operation has modified entry attributes, and that the data is an entry attributes instance.

items.name: static let extractBegin: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the extraction operation has began, this is the first message for this entry.

items.name: static let extractEnd: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the extraction operation has ended, this is the last message for this entry.

items.name: static let extractFail: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the extraction operation has failed, this is the last message for this entry.

items.name: static let extractXAT: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the extraction operation has modified entry extended attributes, and that the data is an entry extended attributes blob.

items.name: static let processExclude: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the process operation has skipped this entry and that the data is an archive header instance.

items.name: static let searchExclude: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the operation has excluded the entry, specified by path, in search.

items.name: static let searchFail: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the operation has reported an error in search.

items.name: static let searchPruneDirectory: ArchiveHeader.EntryMessage
items.desc: An entry message indicating the operation has skipped the directory, specified by path, in search.

items.name: var description: String
items.desc: A textual representation of this instance.
